Death, Destruction, Freedom...It All Starts With Origin Comic #1! 

 
Inspired by community members who attend and participate in our weekly “Lore Games” events, Adult Fantasy Origin Comic #1 features the intolerable Dee-Void and signals the official kickoff of the Adult Fantasy Universe lore!

 
Written by: Zackery Arbela | Art by: Avery Butterworth | Letters by: Eric Weathers | Variant Cover by: Todd Wahnish
